   <p>
    Not sure if summer is right for you? Estimate your cost and financial aid for Summer Sessions, Summer Abroad, 
        or Global Internships. New and Continuing students log into
    <a href="https://calcentral.berkeley.edu/" target="_blank">
     Cal Central
    </a>
    , go to My Finances, navigate to the Finances Resources area on the right side of the page. 
        Scroll down to the Summer Sessions heading and click on Summer Cost and Aid Estimator
   </p>
   <p>
    Please choose either the
    <strong>
     Dependent
    </strong>
    or
    <strong>
     Independent
    </strong>
    estimator to continue:
   </p>
   <ul id="dependency-choice">
    <li>
     <a href="Dependent.aspx" id="mainContent_A1">
