   </ul>
   <p>
    Students who are less than 24 years old may still qualify for Independent status. For more information,
    <a href="http://studentaid.ed.gov/fafsa/filling-out/dependency" target="_blank">
     view the Dependency Status criteria
    </a>
    .
   </p>
